{"tid":2027952,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中共不戰而屈人兵","createTime":"2020-05-21T14:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T15:30:56.000Z","uid":235665,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"edc181455fd4b97cd7cb6d2d4cc39336bf1e26df","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:52:23.000Z","msg":"習大大控制香港，攬炒成功了，美國出手了。<br />\n<br />\n依個諗法其實好危險，散播失敗氣氛，結果就係無左革命精神，以為已經輸曬屈服。<br />\n<br />\n外國見中共改個法例就頹曬，仲點幫得落手？佢地侵犯左法律，令到香港人退無可退，更加要反抗。<br />\n<br />\n而家個個歡迎中共一國一制，接受大陸插手，以為係攬炒，其實係叫人拎把刀拮入d, 係戇居。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAlinsky曾經寫過：革命存在於人民既心靈和思想中。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果個個都因為中共權力而屈服，內心既革命思想就會腐朽，然後慢慢無人提起，變曬愚民。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就算火焰完全熄滅，都唔可以放棄重燃既意志。返校提過：是忘記了？還是害怕想起？<br />\n<br />\n如果我地每一代都因為害怕而封口，之後一代就會忘記，自由就會斷送係意志薄弱既人手上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家做到：即使中共完全操控香港，都堅持示威運動、發表反抗宣言。<br />\n<br />\n死，都要堅守信仰。<br />\n<br />\n無論係對屋企人、朋友、親戚、同事。都唔好因為左迎合而講出違背自己既說話。<br />\n<br />\n士可殺，不可辱。<br />\n寧為玉碎，不為瓦全，先係真正既攬炒！<br />\n<br />\n香港人，抗戰到底！"},{"pid":"0f6de51006385dd416684bb88c0e521df8ae1f5c","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"三分鐘熱度抗爭係無可能，疫症轉淡，要醒啦。"},{"pid":"06b6a456486771f95755352ef8d998c84568eb85","tid":2027952,"uid":230039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"死，都要堅守信仰。"},{"pid":"481bb141a851e2765ce360b0abebc784c1dfaaf9","tid":2027952,"uid":230039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab2a4c46ab32dc661e8e70ec4a477272b85acc63","tid":2027952,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzfhU83.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzfhU83.gif&h=a515fbf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e26517e8d6fc420fd5b81db404b9e7001d014b6","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b6a456486771f95755352ef8d998c84568eb85","tid":2027952,"uid":230039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"死，都要堅守信仰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"多謝你。"},{"pid":"4a3390c478751668362f33afb936e406c96333c1","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab2a4c46ab32dc661e8e70ec4a477272b85acc63","tid":2027952,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzfhU83.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzfhU83.gif&h=a515fbf9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:01:14.000Z","msg":"就算有無通過法例，都唔應該放棄抗爭意識。"},{"pid":"a3c2e8e5b35e140567e3b7c291c98a2fc1e40d22","tid":2027952,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"講得好 意志要長存"},{"pid":"e5cda6f570f6fc9e1e041b996939388eb137421a","tid":2027952,"uid":229185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAjOhvL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAjOhvL.png&h=cef1f057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sK2PMo6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsK2PMo6.png&h=cff9e970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人遇到肺炎都要去旅行，好感動"},{"pid":"91210b5e2cc24c7b1a38fec0c5adc416e876391f","tid":2027952,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:05:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab67900add3d59b5ec761cb019c771ef9cc64b69","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3c2e8e5b35e140567e3b7c291c98a2fc1e40d22","tid":2027952,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"講得好 意志要長存"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:07:51.000Z","msg":"點解外國可以做到，就係人地有民族主體性，我地香港人都值得擁有民族意識。點解新疆同蒙古要逼到中共用武力，就係有獨特既民族主體性。<br />\n<br />\n人係會死，但係民族意識係可以透過教育下一代而延續。跨越生死既界限。"},{"pid":"528dbb40b4fa012206efe05b37364cc802ae0c60","tid":2027952,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"我唔怕冇自由<br />\n係怕大家灰心失意"},{"pid":"f0c05e314101bb5f82cf30de27c35d5f0b6b2a62","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5cda6f570f6fc9e1e041b996939388eb137421a","tid":2027952,"uid":229185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TAjOhvL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTAjOhvL.png&h=cef1f057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sK2PMo6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsK2PMo6.png&h=cff9e970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人遇到肺炎都要去旅行，好感動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:09:47.000Z","msg":"樹大總有枯枝，但係唔可以見人係咁就覺得自己可以咁。每個人都值得擁有獨立思想。"},{"pid":"86df90e76f98f9e5e51b53f309b00e9bd53065fb","tid":2027952,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c66b224915b9c978970d99b6bbb386c4a2cd05","tid":2027952,"uid":235665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"